### Code Conventions

All conventions from .cursorrules apply. Key additions:

- Cloud Vision is a remote API call — no model initialization, no memory overhead on our server
- All OCR processing runs in FastAPI BackgroundTasks
- Mock mode: when OPENAI_API_KEY not set, return hardcoded W2 data. When GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS not set, return hardcoded OCR output.
- Tax calculations use integer arithmetic (cents). No floats. Ever.
- All monetary display uses CurrencyDisplay component with count-up animation
- Use `make` commands for dev workflow (see Makefile at repo root)
- Production infrastructure defined in render.yaml — changes go through PR review

## Quality Gate (Pre-Merge Checklist)

Before merging any PR:
- [ ] All tests pass (`make test`)
- [ ] Lints clean (`make lint`)
- [ ] No PII in logs (grep for SSN patterns)
- [ ] No hardcoded secrets or API keys
- [ ] Mobile tested at 375px (if frontend changes)
- [ ] Acceptance criteria from docs/TASKS.md met

